body.description: Create your own PAW Patrol: Jungle Pups adventures with the PAW Patrol Collectible Figure Gift Pack! This PAW Patrol toy figures set includes Ryder and his PAWsome pups, Chase, Marshall, Rocky, Rubble, Zuma, Tracker and Skye action figures that you won’t find anywhere else! This exciting action figures gift set is the perfect way to bring home all of your favorite characters from the show! Featuring authentic design and styling, each pup looks just like they do in the show, with realistic fur details that will bring each pretend play adventure to life. Use your imagination to re-create your favorite scenes from PAW Patrol: Jungle Pups or create entirely new missions! For even more fun and exciting PAW Patrol series-inspired missions, collect all the PAW Patrol Jungle Pups toys and the PAW Patrol: The Mighty Movie toys, like the awesome Aircraft Carrier HQ and all the special edition PAW patrol toys for girls and boys, like the Mighty Pups, Aqua Pups and Big Truck Pups toy figures and playsets (each sold separately). With PAW Patrol preschool toys, a kid can explore her or her imagination, and develop their motor skills through pretend play, as they relive their favorite scenes from the shows. Enjoy endless PAWsome adventures with the Jungle Pups figure gift set!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect gift for a 3 year old!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I am really pleased with this Paw Patrol Jungle Pups fire truck. It is a gift for my nephew, who turns three next month and it’s entirely age-appropriate. He watches Paw Patrol and is obsessed with fire trucks so this will be a hit for sure. It’s a sturdy, colorful, well-made toy. Placing the water balls in the launcher is great for small muscle coordination. And running to retrieve all the balls or just pushing the truck to a pretend fire might tire him out enough to take a nap. It is the type of simple interactive toy he likes best. His parents will like that it requires no assembly, no batteries or charging, makes no electronic noises and the water balls store neatly in the tank in back.The instructions warn of choking hazards, but those plastic balls are pretty big as is the action figure, so I’m not really seeing it as potentially hazardous. However, there should be some adult supervision with this toy so it is not aimed at pets or siblings. Plus, dogs could do a number on those balls if they think this is a fetch game for them.I am excited about finding the perfect gift and highly recommend this toy

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hours of fun
reviews.reviewText: I gave this truck to my three year old on a day we were expecting company, and I was busy preparing food and cleaning the house. He loved it, and it not only kept him busy while I was working, he played with it all evening while the guests were conversing. This is a lot of fun because it not only encourages imaginative play, but it also encourages movement and physics reasoning skills. At first my son just launched the balls down the hallway, but later he figured out that if he positioned the truck in just the right spot, he could consistently launch balls into a bucket. He spent a good portion of the evening running up and down the hallway retrieving and launching balls and repositioning his bucket. I didn't notice him playing much with the figurine of Chase, but he was excited when he first saw the familiar pup from Paw Patrol. This is a very engaging, fun toy.

reviews.reviewTitle: Son bonitos, listos para la selva
reviews.reviewText: La Patrulla Canina (Paw Patrol en inglés) es una serie de televisión de dibujos animados, muy popular.Incluye 8 figuras: los perritos Zuma, Rocky, Skye/Stella, Tracker, Chase, Marshall/Marcus, Rubble/Rubén y Ryder, el chico líder de la patrulla.Todos llevan su uniforme para la selva. Los cachorros miden 6 cm de alto y solo tienen articulado el cuello, lo cual permite que se pueda girar la cabeza hacia los lados. Ryder mide 9 cm de alto y tiene articulaciones en el cuello, hombros y piernas.Es chulo este set, muy recomendable para los fans de la serie.Espero que mi reseña te haya sido útil. 😊

Mon fils est fan de Pat Patrouille depuis pas mal de temps déjà et il a été fou d ejoie en découvrant ce joli pack.La boîte en elle-même est joli, il a même tenu à la conserver .les figurines sont très jolies et fidèles aux personnages de l'animé .Un superbe petit pack à offrir aux enfants fans de cette série ♥

reviews.reviewTitle: Muy buenos acabados. A los niños les encanta.
reviews.reviewText: A los entusiastas de este tipo de juguetes seguro que les va a encantar este set con 8 figuras de la patrulla canina.Viene estupendamente presentado, ideal también para un regalo y las figuras están hechas con unos detalles muy precisos y de gran calidad en sus acabados.Tienen un tamaño muy adecuado para que los niños los puedan manejar bien.Lo que es indiscutible es que todas las figuras son muy "cuquis", con colores vivos y detalles muy conseguidos, por eso darán mucho juego a los pequeños que podrán echar mano de su imaginación para inventar historias y aventuras con sus personajes preferidos.La única pega que le pongo es que me parece que tiene un precio algo elevado, pero por lo demás está perfecto.

Lot de 8 figurines Pat Patrouille très sympa!La finition est soignée.Elles tiennent debout (enfin.... sur leurs 4 pattes!)Un personnage humain vient enrichir les 1000 histoires que l'enfant pourra s'inventer.La préhension est top et donc conseillée dès 3 ans.J'ai enlevé 1 étoile car je trouve que le prix est tout de même un peu salé.Mais rien à redire sur la qualité du produit!(sans parler de l'esprit sain et positif de ce dessin animé, à recommander!)

8 figurines du célèbre dessin animé Pat Patrouille, mon fils de 3 ans grand fan de la série est heureux comme tout .Cet ensemble est très bien fait, de bonne qualité, les personnages font de 3 à 4 cm, bien peint.Je recommande sans soucis et suis pleinement satisfaite.
